Send a telegram to party branches across a state, rallying members around a specific message or cause. Quick communication to coordinate the movement.

Which state's branches should receive our telegram?

- @nsw: New South Wales
- @vic: Victoria
- @qld: Queensland
- @sa: South Australia
- @wa: Western Australia
- @tas: Tasmania
- @no_telegram: Don't send telegram

