What message should we telegraph to NSW branches?

- @nsw_unity: Unity and solidarity
- @nsw_anticommunist: Vigilance against communists
- @nsw_election: Prepare for electoral work
- @nsw_industrial: Support workers' struggles

@nsw_unity
on-arrival: centre_federal_strength += 0.3; centre_unity_strength += 0.4; right_alp_nsw_dissent -= 1; left_nsw_dissent -= 1; resources -= 0

**TELEGRAM TO NSW BRANCHES STOP UNITY IS OUR STRENGTH STOP LABOR MUST STAND TOGETHER STOP FACTIONALISM SERVES ONLY OUR ENEMIES STOP SOLIDARITY FOREVER STOP**

Our message of unity resonates across NSW branches. Party discipline strengthens, and factional tensions ease slightly.

@nsw_anticommunist
