**TELEGRAM TO NSW BRANCHES STOP REMAIN VIGILANT AGAINST COMMUNIST INFILTRATION STOP LABOR PRINCIPLES NOT MOSCOW ORDERS STOP REPORT SUSPICIOUS ACTIVITY STOP UNITY UNDER LABOR BANNER STOP**

The anti-communist message emboldens the Right and Groupers, but the Left faction is furious at what they call "red-baiting hysteria."

